headline: University of Rochester Medical Center and GE HealthCare form seven-year Care Alliance to build advanced capabilities across system
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., December 03, 2025--University of Rochester Medical Center (URMC) and GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) announce a Care Alliance to build advanced capabilities across URMC’s footprint in upstate New York, including a center of excellence in its Imaging Sciences department, the addition of diagnostic tracer production for molecular imaging applications, and the standardization of patient monitoring across the entire UR Medicine health system.
